OL,5, A host of Wales' most famous artists   
OL,6, have criticised cuts to the Welsh      
OL,7, National Opera (WNO).                  
OL,9,FA protest letter, signed by the likes  
OL,10,Fof Sir Bryn Terfel, Katherine Jenkins, 
OL,11,FMichael Sheen and Ruth Jones, has been 
OL,12,Fsent to First Minister Vaughan Gething.
OL,14,FIt says funding cuts from Arts Council 
OL,15,Fof Wales and Arts Council England (ACE)
OL,16,Fwould be "devastating".                
OL,18,FACE said its commitment to WNO was     
OL,19,F"unwavering". Arts Council Wales has   
OL,20,Fbeen asked to comment.                 
